lyrics:
Yo, I step up on the mic, it's time to set it right,
Spit these words so cold, they'll freeze the night.
From the streets to the stage, I'm the voice of the unheard,
Every lyric I spit, it's like a truth unperturbed.

Born in the struggle, raised in the pain,
But I flipped the script, now I'm breaking these chains.
Rhythm in my veins, beats in my heart,
I'm tearing down walls, I'm tearing 'em apart.
